### 4.4 Script d'automatisation (`scripts/codespace-worker.sh`)

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Lance un worker n8n dans un Codespace connecte a la VM
# Pre-requis : reverse tunnel actif (voir 4.2 Option A)

echo "Starting n8n worker (concurrency=5)..."
n8n worker --concurrency 5 &

echo "Worker PID: $!"
echo "Connected to Redis at localhost:6379 (tunneled to VM)"
echo "Ready to process queue jobs."
```

