### 4.6 Controle depuis la VM (Termius)

```bash
# Lister les Codespaces actifs (necessite gh CLI)
TOKEN=$(git remote get-url origin | sed 's|https://[^:]*:\([^@]*\)@.*|\1|')
curl -s -H "Authorization: token $TOKEN" \
  "https://api.github.com/user/codespaces" | \
  python3 -c "import json,sys; [print(c['name'], c['state']) for c in json.load(sys.stdin)['codespaces']]"

# Arreter un Codespace (annuler un test en cours)
curl -s -X POST -H "Authorization: token $TOKEN" \
  "https://api.github.com/user/codespaces/<name>/stop"

# Ou via gh CLI si installe
gh codespace list
gh codespace stop -c <name>
```

